'''Rafael Candelas Salinas''' (born 21 November 1969) is a [[Mexican people|Mexican]] politician affiliated with the [[Party of the Democratic Revolution]]. As of 2014 he served as Deputy of the [[LIX Legislature of the Mexican Congress]] representing [[Zacatecas]] as replacement of [[Amalia Garc√≠a]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Perfil del legislador|url=http://sil.gobernacion.gob.mx/Librerias/pp_PerfilLegislador.php?SID=&Referencia=926087|publisher=Legislative Information System|accessdate=1 May 2014}}</ref>

